featured_reviews.review_id:
Earlier when I came to Ujhani, this mosque used to look so old and it had small area for performing salah, but now when I came to Ujhani I was surprised to see the new structure. Now, this mosque looks marvelous from inside and outside.
Only one thing which disappointed me a lot that is "Firqa parasti" of the people of Ujhani. Therefore, In this mosque you will only find Barelvi Imam and Muqtadi.

featured_reviews.review_id: The name of this mosque is "Masjid Ahle-hadees". If you are Ahle hadees then this mosque is specially for you, but if you aren't then you may feel something new or awkward because of some masail. For instance, after Surah Fatiha they say Aameen loudly etc. Overall, this is the place of worship, everyone can pray in this mosque because mosque are for everyone.
